# Deeply nested namespace creation

admin 'CREATE NAMESPACE a::b::c'
replicate
---
version: 2

query 'FROM system::namespaces FILTER {name == "a" or name == "a::b" or name == "a::b::c"} SORT {name:ASC}'
---
